<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Your Ticket for {{ event.getTitle() }}!</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Your Ticket for {{ event.getTitle() }}!</h1>
    <p>Hello {{ user.getUsername() }},</p>
    <p>Thank you for purchasing a ticket for the event "{{ event.getTitle() }}".</p>
    <p>Here are the details of your ticket:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Event: {{ event.getTitle() }}</li>
        <li>Ticket ID: {{ ticket.getReference() }}</li>
        <li>Date: {{ ticket.getDay() }}</li>
        <li>Hour: {{ ticket.getHour() }}</li>
        <li>Location: {{ event.getVenue().getName() }}</li>
        <li>Price: {{ event.getPrice()|number_format(2, '.', ',') }} â‚¬</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Please bring this ticket with you to the event.</p>
    <p>Enjoy the event!</p>
</body>
</html>